data.description: This well-maintained 2-story home is a true gem. It boasts an open concept layout with a first-floor bedroom and full bathroom. The entrance features a charming wrap-around porch leading to an office with French doors and a separate entrance. Inside, the kitchen is spacious and well-equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite counters, a tile backsplash, and a breakfast bar on the island. The open living and dining area is roomy, perfect for hosting gatherings. A covered patio and well manicured backyard with a privacy fence make outdoor living inviting. The Taylor Plantation neighborhood offers additional perks, such as nature trails, a clubhouse, a playground, and a community dock along the Ashley River, making it an appealing place to live!There are neighborhood gatherings hosted throughout the year bringing a real sense of community to Taylor Plantation!  Upstairs you will find the large primary suite complete with garden tub, walk-in shower, dual sinks and walk-in closet. Also upstairs are 2 additional bedrooms, hall bathroom and a huge bonus room! The bonus room is currently being used as a 5th bedroom, but would also make a perfect upstairs den, playroom or game room!  The location of this home is ideal being just minutes from Boeing, the Charleston Air Force Base, major highways, shopping and restaurants. It's also zoned for the award winning Dorchester II schools! The elementary and middle schools are just a 3 minute drive or enjoy biking or walking to school! There is so much to love about this home!!
